codec : method for ending and decoding (it is used for both audio and video formats).
container : file format that holder mp4,avi ,etc  (container the actual content)
Bitrate : number of bit process in one second (kbps,mbps,etc)
Resolution : 1920*1080 ......



HSL :Http live streaming (created by apple )
it helps to split video  file into chunks

hsl working in 3 diffrerent parts
1. segmentation : video is split into small segments 2-10 seconds each
2. master PlayList : Here indexing perform (means all segments get some index ) and their file format is .m3u8
3. variant playlist : Here each video quality is level has its own playlist ,listing the URL's  of thier segent at that quality



